Policies for the University of Illinois at Chicago Library





            Library Policies Tiles.
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Code of Conduct
                    

                UIC Library patrons are expected to preserve, protect and respect.
            









                            Collection Development Policy
                    

                UIC Library policy for collection selection, maintenance, haring, etc.
            









                            Daley Library Policies
                    

                Policies for the Richard J. Daley Library
            









                            Daley Library IDEA Commons Classroom Reservations
                    

                Policies for use of IDEA Commons Classroom Reservations
            









                            Digital Project Collaboration Policy
                    

                UIC Library policy on collaborative digital projects.
            









                            Renewal and Return Policies
                    

                UIC Library policies for renewing and returning items.
            









                            Service Policy
                    

                UIC Library policy on services and resources for the support of our user community.
            









                            User Privacy Policy
                    

                The UIC Library respects the privacy of all users.
            










            UIC School of Law Library Policies
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The UIC School of Law Library serves the faculty and students of the UIC School of Law. The Law Library is administered separately from the UIC University Library and has its own access and use policies.






